    <section id="alien-covenant">
        <img src="./images/showcase/aliens.jpg" alt="" />
        <div class="description">
            <p>
              "We built custom software in TouchDesigner to control of 60 screens using 5 media servers and laptops in realtime. HAP Alpha was an ideal choice as it allowed for alpha embedding and gpu optimised playback for multi layer media stacking, up to 8 layers per screen, 4 screens per instance.
              Fast media encoding so files could be quickly modified and supplied on demand throughout the shoot. Low file size which meant files could be distributed onto the media server network quickly."
            </p>
        </div>
        <header>
